sql_json.natural_language: List all emails in the last month where adrian@rancilio.co.za sent an attachment.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE fromEmail = 'adrian@rancilio.co.za' AND hasAttachments = true AND sentAt >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 MONTH) ORDER BY sentAt DESC;
